msgid ""
"All Pyramid-related :term:`deployment settings` (e.g. ``debug_all``, "
"``debug_notfound``) are now meant to be prefixed with the prefix "
"``pyramid.``.  For example: ``debug_all`` -> ``pyramid.debug_all``.  The "
"old non-prefixed settings will continue to work indefinitely but "
"supplying them may print a deprecation warning.  All scaffolds and "
"tutorials have been changed to use prefixed settings."
msgstr ""

#: ../../whatsnew-1.2.rst:196
